{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01W9HkATdoTjhMUGbzixQCra","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully migrated all the barista-service Java files from Jakarta EE/MicroProfile/Open Liberty to Spring Boot 3.2.5. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n## Files Modified/Created:\n\n### 1. **Created: BaristaServiceApplication.java**\n   - **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/barista-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/barista/BaristaServiceApplication.java`\n   - **Changes**: New Spring Boot main application class with `@SpringBootApplication` annotation\n\n### 2. **Deleted: BaristaApplication.java**\n   - **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/barista-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/barista/api/BaristaApplication.java`\n   - **Changes**: Removed JAX-RS Application class (no longer needed in Spring Boot)\n\n### 3. **Rewritten: StatusResource.java**\n   - **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/barista-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/barista/api/StatusResource.java`\n   - **Changes**: \n     - Replaced JAX-RS annotations (`@Path`, `@GET`, `@Produces`) with Spring MVC annotations (`@RestController`, `@RequestMapping`, `@GetMapping`)\n     - Endpoint remains at `/api/status` returning \"barista ok\"\n\n### 4. **Rewritten: BasicHealth.java**\n   - **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/barista-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/barista/health/BasicHealth.java`\n   - **Changes**: \n     - Replaced MicroProfile Health (`HealthCheck`, `@Readiness`) with Spring Boot Actuator (`HealthIndicator`)\n     - Changed from `@ApplicationScoped` to `@Component`\n     - Updated method from `call()` returning `HealthCheckResponse` to `health()` returning Spring's `Health` object\n\n### 5. **Rewritten: BaristaConsumer.java**\n   - **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/barista-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/barista/messaging/BaristaConsumer.java`\n   - **Changes**: \n     - Replaced MicroProfile Reactive Messaging annotations (`@Incoming`, `@Outgoing`) with Spring Kafka (`@KafkaListener`, `KafkaTemplate`)\n     - Changed from `@ApplicationScoped` to `@Component`\n     - Replaced Jakarta JSON-B with Jackson `ObjectMapper` for JSON processing\n     - Updated message handling pattern from reactive streams to Spring Kafka's consumer/producer model\n     - Preserved business logic: receives orders from \"barista-commands\" topic, processes them, and sends status updates to \"order-updates\" topic\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated and are ready for Spring Boot 3.2.5!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b03f3699-6115-4602-aa3a-188761fea59b","uuid":"81852be9-77c7-40ac-a1e8-1d304ebd3a6c"}
