oing`) to Spring Kafka (`@KafkaListener`, `KafkaTemplate`)\n   - Replaced Jakarta JSON-P with Jackson ObjectMapper for JSON processing\n   - Changed from reactive stream processing to imperative Kafka consumer pattern\n\nAll changes maintain the same business logic while adopting Spring Boot 3.2.5 conventions and APIs."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b03f3699-6115-4602-aa3a-188761fea59b","uuid":"3cb33f59-2804-492c-abd5-7068f3a2928f"}
