ltMessage() : \"\"))\n    28→                .toList();\n    29→        return ResponseEntity.badRequest().body(Map.of(\"errors\", errors));\n    30→    }\n    31→\n    32→    private Map<String, String> toEntry(ConstraintViolation<?> v) {\n    33→        String field = v.getPropertyPath() == null ? \"\" : v.getPropertyPath().toString();\n    34→        return Map.of(\"field\", field, \"message\", v.getMessage());\n    35→    }\n    36→}\n    37→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_015FN73awaz9gWcjk1hyAS98","session_id":"b03f3699-6115-4602-aa3a-188761fea59b","uuid":"dc5d158a-7733-41bd-aa22-8c9227b9544b"}
