{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01P657Hh4tk9hJS6f6gLkXaz","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.coffeeshop.orders.messaging;\n     2→\n     3→import com.fasterxml.jackson.core.JsonProcessingException;\n     4→import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper;\n     5→import org.springframework.kafka.core.KafkaTemplate;\n     6→import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n     7→\n     8→@Component\n     9→public class OrdersPipeline {\n    10→\n    11→    private final KafkaTemplate<String, String> kafkaTemplate;\n    12→    private final ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n    13→\n    14→    public OrdersPipeline(KafkaTemplate<String, String> kafkaTemplate, ObjectMapper objectMapper) {\n    15→        this.kafkaTemplate = kafkaTemplate;\n    16→        this.objectMapper = objectMapper;\n    17→    }\n    18→\n    19→    public void publishToBarista(OrderCommand cmd) {\n    20→        try {\n    21→            System.out.println(\"[orders] sending barista command: \" + cmd);\n    22→            kafkaTemplate.send(\"barista-commands\", objectMapper.writeValueAsString(cmd));\n    23→        } catch (JsonProcessingException e) {\n    24→            throw new RuntimeException(\"Failed to serialize barista command\", e);\n    25→        }\n    26→    }\n    27→\n    28→    public void publishToKitchen(OrderCommand cmd) {\n    29→        try {\n    30→            System.out.println(\"[orders] sending kitchen command: \" + cmd);\n    31→            kafkaTemplate.send(\"kitchen-commands\", objectMapper.writeValueAsString(cmd));\n    32→        } catch (JsonProcessingException e) {\n    33→            throw new RuntimeException(\"Failed to serialize kitchen command\", e);\n    34→        }\n    35→    }\n    36→\n    37→    public record OrderCommand(String target, long orderId, String item, int quantity) {}\n    38→}\n    39→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b03f3699-6115-4602-aa3a-188761fea59b","uuid":"026e6f2f-c7be-4c1d-8777-ab61404fa102"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_016BS8F9ETgHakFxEkBbx25u","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is that `kafkaTemplate.send()` returns a `CompletableFuture` but the method waits for it. I need to make this fire-and-forget and catch exceptions gracefully. Let me also read the OrderService to see the flow:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":773,"cache_read_input_tokens":134253,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":773,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":182},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b03f3699-6115-4602-aa3a-188761fea59b","uuid":"595939db-69fc-47a5-8e1a-4b0b7716b735"}
