{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01XykqAzejJnnj1DPNq2KZDr","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.coffeeshop.orders.service;\n     2→\n     3→import com.coffeeshop.common.domain.OrderRequest;\n     4→import com.coffeeshop.orders.domain.OrderEntity;\n     5→import com.coffeeshop.orders.domain.OrderRepository;\n     6→import com.coffeeshop.orders.messaging.OrdersPipeline;\n     7→import jakarta.validation.Valid;\n     8→import org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\n     9→import org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional;\n    10→\n    11→@Service\n    12→public class OrderService {\n    13→    private final OrderRepository repo;\n    14→    private final OrdersPipeline pipeline;\n    15→\n    16→    public OrderService(OrderRepository repo, OrdersPipeline pipeline) {\n    17→        this.repo = repo;\n    18→        this.pipeline = pipeline;\n    19→    }\n    20→\n    21→    @Transactional\n    22→    public String place(@Valid OrderRequest req) {\n    23→        var e = new OrderEntity();\n    24→        e.setCustomer(req.customer());\n    25→        e.setItem(req.item());\n    26→        e.setQuantity(req.quantity());\n    27→        repo.save(e);\n    28→\n    29→        if (isDrink(req.item())) {\n    30→            pipeline.publishToBarista(new OrdersPipeline.OrderCommand(\"BARISTA\", e.getId(), req.item(), req.quantity()));\n    31→        } else {\n    32→            pipeline.publishToKitchen(new OrdersPipeline.OrderCommand(\"KITCHEN\", e.getId(), req.item(), req.quantity()));\n    33→        }\n    34→        return String.valueOf(e.getId());\n    35→    }\n    36→\n    37→    private boolean isDrink(String item) {\n    38→        if (item == null) return false;\n    39→        var s = item.toLowerCase();\n    40→        return s.contains(\"coffee\") || s.contains(\"latte\") || s.contains(\"espresso\")\n    41→                || s.contains(\"cappuccino\") || s.contains(\"americano\") || s.contains(\"mocha\")\n    42→                || s.contains(\"tea\");\n    43→    }\n    44→}\n    45→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b03f3699-6115-4602-aa3a-188761fea59b","uuid":"f20b8323-0039-409c-8937-b003a07f7029"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Y5qEn36X3z92njp3EugGTJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need to make the Kafka publishing fire-and-forget so the order placement succeeds even without a Kafka broker. The original Jakarta/MicroProfile Reactive Messaging was async by design. Let me fix the OrdersPipeline:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1102,"cache_read_input_tokens":135026,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1102,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":699},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b03f3699-6115-4602-aa3a-188761fea59b","uuid":"476a4791-8e98-40d8-a41d-19be13e666a0"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Y5qEn36X3z92njp3EugGTJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01N5UHx6EDUwphUMkAUHSgpQ","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/orders-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/orders/messaging/OrdersPipeline.java","content":"package com.coffeeshop.orders.messaging;\n\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.core.JsonProcessingException;\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper;\nimport org.springframework.kafka.core.KafkaTemplate;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n\n@Component\npublic class OrdersPipeline {\n\n    private final KafkaTemplate<String, String> kafkaTemplate;\n    private final ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n\n    public OrdersPipeline(KafkaTemplate<String, String> kafkaTemplate, ObjectMapper objectMapper) {\n        this.kafkaTemplate = kafkaTemplate;\n        this.objectMapper = objectMapper;\n    }\n\n    public void publishToBarista(OrderCommand cmd) {\n        try {\n            System.out.println(\"[orders] sending barista command: \" + cmd);\n            String json = objectMapper.writeValueAsString(cmd);\n            kafkaTemplate.send(\"barista-commands\", json)\n                    .whenComplete((result, ex) -> {\n                        if (ex != null) {\n                            System.err.println(\"[orders] failed to send barista command: \" + ex.getMessage());\n                        }\n                    });\n        } catch (JsonProcessingException e) {\n            System.err.println(\"[orders] failed to serialize barista command: \" + e.getMessage());\n        }\n    }\n\n    public void publishToKitchen(OrderCommand cmd) {\n        try {\n            System.out.println(\"[orders] sending kitchen command: \" + cmd);\n            String json = objectMapper.writeValueAsString(cmd);\n            kafkaTemplate.send(\"kitchen-commands\", json)\n                    .whenComplete((result, ex) -> {\n                        if (ex != null) {\n                            System.err.println(\"[orders] failed to send kitchen command: \" + ex.getMessage());\n                        }\n                    });\n        } catch (JsonProcessingException e) {\n            System.err.println(\"[orders] failed to serialize kitchen command: \" + e.getMessage());\n        }\n    }\n\n    public record OrderCommand(String target, long orderId, String item, int quantity) {}\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1102,"cache_read_input_tokens":135026,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1102,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":699},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b03f3699-6115-4602-aa3a-188761fea59b","uuid":"e0ba3d32-eee9-4e92-a187-c05e0c97a27c"}
