{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01LXMJz27egdpEZ3Xhb7LbvE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migration is complete. Here is the final report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n- **Frameworks involved:** Jakarta EE 10 / MicroProfile 6.1 / Open Liberty -> Spring Boot 3.2.5\n- **High-level actions:** Replaced all Jakarta EE + MicroProfile APIs with Spring Boot equivalents, migrated from WAR-on-Liberty to fat JAR, converted reactive messaging to Spring Kafka, moved from manual JPA to Spring Data JPA, replaced MicroProfile Health with Spring Boot Actuator\n- **Overall outcome:** **Success** - 8/8 smoke tests passing\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Spring Boot parent, module aggregator\n- common/pom.xml: Minimal deps (validation-api, jackson)\n- orders-service/pom.xml: Spring Boot starters (web, data-jpa, validation, actuator, kafka, h2, postgresql)\n- barista-service/pom.xml: Spring Boot starters (web, actuator, kafka)\n- kitchen-service/pom.xml: Spring Boot starters (web, actuator, kafka)\n- Dockerfile: Build Spring Boot fat JAR, run with java -jar\n- orders-service/Dockerfile: Same pattern\n- barista-service/Dockerfile: Same pattern\n- kitchen-service/Dockerfile: Same pattern\n- orders-service/.../web/OrdersResource.java: JAX-RS -> Spring MVC\n- orders-service/.../web/ConstraintViolationExceptionMapper.java: @Provider -> @RestControllerAdvice\n- orders-service/.../domain/OrderRepository.java: Manual JPA -> Spring Data JPA\n- orders-service/.../service/OrderService.java: @ApplicationScoped -> @Service\n- orders-service/.../messaging/OrdersPipeline.java: MicroProfile Reactive -> Spring Kafka\n- orders-service/.../messaging/OrderUpdatesListener.java: @Incoming -> @KafkaListener\n- orders-service/.../health/BasicHealth.java: MicroProfile Health -> Actuator\n- barista-service/.../api/StatusResource.java: JAX-RS -> Spring MVC\n- barista-service/.../health/BasicHealth.java: MicroProfile