m.xml files for Spring Boot 3.2.5\n[2026-03-14T06:39:00Z] [info] Refactored all orders-service Java files (8 files modified/created, 3 deleted)\n[2026-03-14T06:40:00Z] [info] Refactored all barista-service Java files (4 files modified/created, 1 deleted)\n[2026-03-14T06:40:30Z] [info] Refactored all kitchen-service Java files (4 files modified/created, 1 deleted)\n[2026-03-14T06:41:00Z] [info] Created application.properties for all 3 services\n[2026-03-14T06:42:00Z] [info] Moved static assets from webapp/ to resources/static/\n[2026-03-14T06:43:00Z] [info] Updated all 4 Dockerfiles for Spring Boot fat JAR\n[2026-03-14T06:44:00Z] [info] Generated smoke.py with 8 test cases\n[2026-03-14T06:45:00Z] [info] Docker build succeeded on first attempt\n[2026-03-14T06:46:00Z] [info] Container started, Spring Boot up in 8.4s\n[2026-03-14T06:48:00Z] [warning] Kafka blocking caused 500 errors on order creation\n[2026-03-14T06:49:00Z] [info] Fixed: Added try-catch + async Kafka + fail-fast producer config\n[2026-03-14T06:52:00Z] [info] Rebuilt and restarted container\n[2026-03-14T06:53:00Z] [info] All 8 smoke tests passing - migration complete\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 1 warning resolved (Kafka blocking send)\n- **Critical Issues:** None\n- **Resolution:** Made Kafka publishing fire-and-forget with try-catch in OrderService and async callbacks in OrdersPipeline. Added `max.block.ms=5000` to prevent 60s blocking."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":385,"cache_read_input_tokens":126563,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":385,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1623},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b03f3699-6115-4602-aa3a-188761fea59b","uuid":"b07005f7-6329-45c7-aae2-4bb45fab3786"}
